.s329: PUT .outpe 329 116
.s330: PUT .outpe 330 101
.s331: PUT .outpe 331 120
.s332: PUT .outpe 332 116
.s337: PUT .outpe 337 2
.s341: PUT .outpe 341 16
.s345: PUT .outpe 345 2
.s349: PUT .outpe 349 2
.s364: PUT .outpe 364 32
.s367: PUT .outpe 367 96

